name: Cute Puppy
description:
Cute and Trendy world on the Blockchain - Coin & Collectibles

Cute Puppy is made out of love, trust and respect by a community of puppies’ lovers. 

Cute Puppy is composed of a cryptocurrency called PUPS, a collection of unique arts called POO and a decentralized exchange called WOOF for puppies (and puppies’ owners).
